"权限模型如何控制记忆的读写？\"]","run_status":"waiting","sort":0,"summary":"该文档是Agent记忆体系技术落地方案，面向开发落地，基于现有53AIHub架构。不依赖runtimev2，不重写relay主链路，不替代现有知识库和技能库，优先做增量模型、服务和注入层。核心概念包括Memory（长期记忆）、Memory Candidate（候选记忆）、Memory Policy（策略）、Memory Packet（上下文包）和Memory Event（审计事件）。数据模型设计包括agent_memories、agent_memory_candidates、agent_memory_events和agent_memory_policies四张表。权限模型定义了读取、写入、删除和停用的规则。记忆注入链路在relay组装请求上下文时接入，通过MemoryPacketService构建MemoryPacket。","type":1,"updated_time":1778251201803,"upload_file":null,"upload_file_id":4150,"upload_source":"local","user_id":2401},{"ai_generate_chunk_status":"inactive","ai_generate_sq_status":"inactive","character_count":1104,"cleaning_rule_info":"","config_id":null,"conversion_status":"normal","created_time":1778225057612,"deleted_at":0,"deleted_by":0,"eid":"RWxeNh","id":"tz4yJw","insight_summary":"","is_active_deleted":false,"is_deleted":false,"is_favorite":false,"knowledge_map":"","library_id":"tIMyJw","origin_ref_id":0,"origin_source":"direct","origin_type":"manual_create","parse_type":"","parsing_status":"normal","path":"/1-设计规划文档/已实现/工作AI-前台.md","questions":"","run_status":"not_started","sort":0,"summary":"","type":1,"updated_time":1778225057612,"upload_file":null,"upload_file_id":0,"upload_source":"direct","user_id":2416},{"ai_generate_chunk_status":"inactive","ai_generate_sq_status":"inactive","character_count":952,"cleaning_rule_info":"","config_id":null,"conversion_status":"normal","created_time":1778225013670,"deleted_at":0,"deleted_by":0,"eid":"RWxeNh","id":"owylrK","insight_summary":"","is_active_deleted":false,"is_deleted":false,"is_favorite":false,"knowledge_map":"","library_id":"tIMyJw","origin_ref_id":0,"origin_source":"direct","origin_type":"manual_create","parse_type":"","parsing_status":"normal","path":"/1-设计规划文档/已实现/上传文件时重名.md","questions":"","run_status":"not_started","sort":0,"summary":"","type":1,"updated_time":1778225013670,"upload_file":null,"upload_file_id":0,"upload_source":"direct","user_id":2416},{"ai_generate_chunk_status"