ourceType}:{resourceID}`，采用Read-Through策略，TTL设为5分钟。权限变更时通过UpsertPermission、DeletePermission、UpdateSpacePermissions等操作主动清除缓存。当前仅处理用户维度权限，分组权限依赖TTL自然过期，未来可引入分组缓存或版本控制。","type":1,"updated_time":1778147052714,"upload_file":null,"upload_file_id":4143,"upload_source":"local","user_id":2401},{"ai_generate_chunk_status":"inactive","ai_generate_sq_status":"normal","character_count":0,"cleaning_rule_info":"{\"strategy_id\":\"GZUcnU\",\"strategy_name\":\"通用文档\",\"strategy_icon\":\"\",\"pipeline_id\":\"GZUcnU\",\"pipeline_name\":\"通用文档\",\"pipeline_icon\":\"https://hubapi.53ai.com/api/images/library/pipeline-icon.png.png\",\"run_id\":\"1c15f9c7-a169-4324-ae2d-be11eb581e77\",\"status\":\"waiting\",\"progress\":83,\"success_count\":5,\"failure_count\":0,\"total_steps\":6,\"start_time\":1778147052887,\"end_time\":0,\"current_job_type\":\"\",\"next_step_key\":\"graph_generation\",\"next_step_name\":\"graph_generation\",\"next_step_mode\":\"manual\"}","config_id":null,"conversion_status":"normal","created_time":1778147052769,"deleted_at":0,"deleted_by":0,"eid":"RWxeNh","id":"sWB8ja","insight_summary":"","is_active_deleted":false,"is_deleted":false,"is_favorite":false,"knowledge_map":"","library_id":"tIMyJw","origin_ref_id":"IxPrvB","origin_source":"local","origin_type":"personal_upload","parse_type":"","parsing_status":"normal","path":"/2-开发文档/权限性能优化/permission_current_state_and_optimization_plan.md","questions":"[\"当前权限系统的主要性能瓶颈是什么？\",\"Phase1优化方案包括哪些具体措施？\",\"前后端接口协作建议如何解决N+1问题？\"]","run_status":"waiting","sort":0,"summary":"本文档分析53AIHub知识库权限系统现状与优化规划。核心问题：文档权限多层资源继承（文档→父文件夹→知识库→空间）和主体多层关系（用户→组→部门映射→公司），前端“查文件”和“查权限”分离导致高频N+1查询。优化分三阶段：Phase1增批量接口、列表直出权限、缓存有效主体集合和文件祖先链；Phase2引入权限索引表异步增量维护；Phase3引入ReBAC/Zanzibar架构。目标降低P95延迟40%+、减少SQL次数60%+，保证误判率为0。","type":1,"updated_time":1778147052769,"upload_file":null,"upload_file_id":4144,"upload_source":"local","user_id":2401},{"ai_generate_chunk_status":"inactive","ai_generate_sq_status":"normal","character_count":0,"cleaning_rule_info":"{\"s